          <div class="text">
            <p><b>Doing business should be about doing the right thing by the client/customer, not making money.</b></p>
            <p>Granted, we are in it for the money too, but the money is of less importance, the client/customer comes first.</p>
            <p>Too many other providers put profit over the ones giving them that profit, and this has to stop!</p>
            <p>It's very true that you can do almost anything with the right amount of money, and this is something our competitors have learned. The ones with the bigger pockets buy out the smaller guys when they struggle, and then the customer/client doesn't actually know who the actual provider is.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
          
        <div class="statement">
