            <p><b>Persona Clix will Never be Sold!</b></p>
            <p>I have spent too long building a brand and a quality service to let it fall into the hands of someone with big pockets. If the service gets to a point where it struggles, we will tell you about it, and would rather close down than sell.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
          
        <div class="statement">
