          <div class="text">
            <p><b>Persona Clix will Always be Honest!</b></p>
            <p>Our competitors would rather read from a script whenever you ask a question, and blame the customer or other systems to hide the mistakes they make themselves.</p>
            <p>We believe in always giving care and attention into every response given to a client, and do our best to ensure the client has as many facts as possible to help them make an informed decision. Sometimes things do go wrong, and should that happen and it affects you, we will hold our hands up and apologise and do our best to put it right.</p>
            <p>The price you pay will not be the cheapest or most expensive you can find, but what we believe is a fair and honest price.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
          
