            <p><b>Persona Clix will Never Tie You In!</b></p>
            <p>Part of the reason some of our competitors have such large pockets is because they legally prevent their customers from leaving once signed up because they signed a contract with a minimum duration.</p>
            <p>When you sign up to a service from Persona Clix, there is no contract, meaning you are free to leave whenever you want, and as an added bonus, you do not even need to give notice or reason. Depending on the situation, you may also be entitled to a refund.</p>
